@page "/privacy"

<PageTitle>Privacy Policy - TodoX</PageTitle>

<MudContainer MaxWidth="MaxWidth.Medium" Class="py-8">
    <MudPaper Class="todox-card pa-6" rounded="true">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h4" Class="todox-page-title">Privacy Policy</MudText>
        <MudText Typo="Typo.caption" Class="todox-page-subtitle">Last updated: July 2026</MudText>

        <MudDivider Class="my-4" />

        <MudStack Spacing="3">
            <MudText>
                TodoX provides tools for customers to manage social pages, generate AI content, render videos,
                and publish content to connected channels such as Facebook Pages, Instagram accounts, and TikTok accounts.
            </MudText>

            <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">Information We Collect</MudText>
            <MudText>
                We may collect account information such as name, email, customer profile, connected page identifiers,
                page names, access tokens authorized by the user, publishing logs, render job metadata, and activity logs
                required to operate the TodoX service.
            </MudText>

            <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">How We Use Information</MudText>
            <MudText>
                We use the information to authenticate users, connect and manage social pages, publish content at the
                user's request, show page status, provide customer support, secure the system, and maintain audit logs.
            </MudText>

            <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">Facebook and Instagram Data</MudText>
            <MudText>
                When users connect Facebook or Instagram, TodoX only uses permissions granted by the user to list
                pages/accounts, read basic engagement/page metadata, and publish content selected or created by the user.
                TodoX does not sell user data.
            </MudText>

            <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">Data Sharing</MudText>
            <MudText>
                We do not sell personal data. Data may be processed by infrastructure providers, hosting services,
                AI providers, storage services, or social platform APIs only as necessary to provide the TodoX service.
            </MudText>

            <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">Data Security</MudText>
            <MudText>
                TodoX uses access control, authentication, audit logs, and secure storage practices to protect user data.
                Social access tokens should only be used for authorized actions requested by the user.
            </MudText>

            <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">Data Deletion</MudText>
            <MudText>
                Users can request deletion of their account data and connected social data by following the instructions
                at <MudLink Href="/data-deletion">User Data Deletion</MudLink>.
            </MudText>

            <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">Contact</MudText>
            <MudText>For privacy requests, contact TodoX support at: support@todox.vn</MudText>
        </MudStack>
    </MudPaper>
</MudContainer>
